The white trailer had no markings and Kvapil believes the person who stole it probably had no idea what they were really nabbing, he told ESPN. 

'There's a lot of money inside that little trailer right now,' he said. 'For the team's sake and John Cohen's sake, hopefully the parts and pieces can be recovered or it will be a really huge setback.' 

